This is some fun project i did in the past.
I remember someone showing me an entire drawing of mona lisa in microsoft excel
I said i can do the same but with html tables (Obviously i can not, manually)
He didn't believe me so i decided to make this converter.

How it works:

- It takes a base64 WITHOUT HEADERS
- Once you leave the textarea it will try to parse it into a table.

The original image will be shown at the beggining of the page.
